From David Prutchi Subject Re Flexible solar cells In article A Wayne Dawe writes Two or three years ago I saw a report on TV about a company that had developed a method of making solar cells on a flexible substrate My failing memory has convinced me it was some flexible metal I now have an application that requires a flexible solar cell and was hoping someone out in netland knows something about this company or a similar product Any help would be greatly appreciated Wayne Dawe pick a path, any path but don't send me anything bigger than K wayne r node UUCP Wayne Look for these advertised in sailboat supplies catalogs and sail related magazines eg SAIL David Prutchi HC DT Washington University Campus Box One Brookings Drive St Louis, MO